[umm Angel Prime took the hit for Tavatron. but next time please read 
my post.]



Angel Prime/Starwind/Steed/Rattrap/Depth Charge/Blade Runner



Angel Prime opened a com to a couple of the maximals. [the names are 
up top.] after giving them there orders they did what he said. Depth 
Charge was about to start to argue but he knew this was not the time.


Angel Prime flew infront of Unicron. Starwind changed to his space 
ship mode and let Steed and Rattrap get on top of him. he lfew up 
behind Unicron. Depth Charge flew up on the left side of him. Blade 
Runner flew on the right side. all of them were prepared to attack at 
any second they saw it fit to. Starwind turned the tracking system on 
Unicron so he could fire missles. Then Angel Prime yelled out loud 
enough so everyone could here.



Angel Prime:



"leave Unicron alone we will deal with him. [then he turned to 
Unicron.] well there is only one way out and that is through us. Bring 
it."




Angel Prime's fire started to go around him. [like powering up.]
